## File Naming Conventions

For authentic Win31 feel:
- All caps: `README.TXT`, `INSTALL.EXE`
- 8.3 format: `PROGRAM.EXE`, `CONFIG.SYS`
- Extensions matter: `.WRI`, `.BMP`, `.INI`

